Get exclusive access to exciting content and our entire DVD library all while helping to support us at https://patreon.com/fountainview
Twice a year, Fountainview Academy hosts a Week of Prayer. This time of prayer and spiritual focus is always a blessing for all participating faculty and students. We hope to share our enthusiasm and love for this event through this live stream.
